I have shown how to use Pipeline and Columtransformer for the  effective DS steps.
Note:
1. Always create sperate Pipeline for numerical  values and complete all your transoformation sepereately
2. I have  shown both the Loose  method and Effective  method for using it.
3. Transfromation used:
a. SimpleImpter for missing variable -Both character and numeric
b. RobustScaler for Scaling of numeric variables
c. OnehotEncoding for the character variables
